{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I run a design studio in New York."},{"time":3000,"text":"Every seven years, I close it for one year"},{"time":7000,"text":"to pursue"},{"time":10000,"text":"some little experiments, things that"},{"time":12000,"text":"are always difficult to accomplish"},{"time":15000,"text":"during the regular working year."},{"time":17000,"text":"In that year, we are not available"},{"time":19000,"text":"for any of our clients."},{"time":21000,"text":"We are totally closed."},{"time":24000,"text":"And as you can imagine,"},{"time":26000,"text":"it is a lovely and very energetic time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"I originally had opened the studio in New York"},{"time":33000,"text":"to combine my two loves, music and design."},{"time":36000,"text":"And we created videos and packaging"},{"time":39000,"text":"for many musicians that you know,"},{"time":41000,"text":"and for even more that you've never heard of."},{"time":45000,"text":"As I realized, just like with many many things in my life"},{"time":49000,"text":"that I actually love,"},{"time":51000,"text":"I adapt to it."},{"time":53000,"text":"And I get, over time, bored by them."},{"time":55000,"text":"And for sure, in our case,"},{"time":58000,"text":"our work started to look the same."},{"time":60000,"text":"You see here a glass eye in a die cut of a book."},{"time":63000,"text":"Quite the similar idea, then, a perfume packaged"},{"time":66000,"text":"in a book, in a die cut."},{"time":70000,"text":"So I decided to close it down for one year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"Also is the knowledge that"},{"time":77000,"text":"right now we spend about"},{"time":79000,"text":"in the first 25 years of our lives learning,"},{"time":83000,"text":"then there is another 40 years"},{"time":85000,"text":"that's really reserved for working."},{"time":88000,"text":"And then tacked on at the end of it"},{"time":90000,"text":"are about 15 years for retirement."},{"time":93000,"text":"And I thought it might be helpful"},{"time":96000,"text":"to basically cut off five of those retirement years"},{"time":100000,"text":"and intersperse them in between those working years."},{"time":106000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":112000,"text":"That's clearly enjoyable for myself."},{"time":114000,"text":"But probably even more important is"},{"time":117000,"text":"that the work that comes out of these years"},{"time":120000,"text":"flows back into the company"},{"time":122000,"text":"and into society at large,"},{"time":124000,"text":"rather than just benefiting a grandchild or two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"There is a fellow TEDster who spoke two years ago,"},{"time":133000,"text":"Jonathan Haidt,"},{"time":135000,"text":"who defined his work into three different levels."},{"time":139000,"text":"And they rang very true for me."},{"time":141000,"text":"I can see my work as a job. I do it for money."},{"time":144000,"text":"I likely already look forward to the weekend on Thursdays."},{"time":148000,"text":"And I probably will need a hobby as a leveling mechanism."},{"time":153000,"text":"In a career I'm definitely more engaged."},{"time":156000,"text":"But at the same time, there will be periods when I think"},{"time":158000,"text":"is all that really hard work really worth my while?"},{"time":163000,"text":"While in the third one, in the calling,"},{"time":165000,"text":"very much likely I would do it also"},{"time":168000,"text":"if I wouldn't be financially compensated for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"I am not a religious person myself,"},{"time":174000,"text":"but I did look for nature."},{"time":177000,"text":"I had spent my first sabbatical in New York City."},{"time":181000,"text":"Looked for something different for the second one."},{"time":184000,"text":"Europe and the U.S. didn't really feel enticing"},{"time":187000,"text":"because I knew them too well. So Asia it was."},{"time":190000,"text":"The most beautiful landscapes I had seen in Asia"},{"time":192000,"text":"were Sri Lanka and Bali."},{"time":194000,"text":"Sri Lanka still had the civil war going on, so Bali it was."},{"time":198000,"text":"It's a wonderful, very craft-oriented society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"I arrived there in September 2008,"},{"time":206000,"text":"and pretty much started to work right away."},{"time":209000,"text":"There is wonderful inspiration coming from the area itself."},{"time":215000,"text":"However the first thing that I needed was"},{"time":218000,"text":"mosquito repellent typography"},{"time":221000,"text":"because they were definitely around heavily."},{"time":224000,"text":"And then I needed some sort of way"},{"time":227000,"text":"to be able to get back to all the wild dogs"},{"time":230000,"text":"that surround my house,"},{"time":232000,"text":"and attacked me during my morning walks."},{"time":235000,"text":"So we created this series of 99 portraits on tee shirts."},{"time":241000,"text":"Every single dog on one tee shirt."},{"time":245000,"text":"As a little retaliation"},{"time":247000,"text":"with a just ever so slightly menacing message"},{"time":251000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":252000,"text":"on the back of the shirt."},{"time":254000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"Just before I left New York"},{"time":258000,"text":"I decided I could actually renovate my studio."},{"time":262000,"text":"And then just leave it all to them."},{"time":265000,"text":"And I don't have to do anything."},{"time":267000,"text":"So I looked for furniture."},{"time":269000,"text":"And it turned out that"},{"time":271000,"text":"all the furniture that I really liked,"},{"time":273000,"text":"I couldn't afford."},{"time":275000,"text":"And all the stuff I could afford, I didn't like."},{"time":277000,"text":"So one of the things that we pursued in Bali"},{"time":279000,"text":"was pieces of furniture."},{"time":282000,"text":"This one, of course, still works with the wild dogs."},{"time":285000,"text":"It's not quite finished yet."},{"time":288000,"text":"And I think by the time this lamp came about,"},{"time":291000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":293000,"text":"I had finally made peace with those dogs."},{"time":297000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"Then there is a coffee table. I also did a coffee table."},{"time":305000,"text":"It's called Be Here Now."},{"time":307000,"text":"It includes 330 compasses."},{"time":311000,"text":"And we had custom espresso cups made"},{"time":314000,"text":"that hide a magnet inside,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and make those compasses go crazy,"},{"time":319000,"text":"always centering on them."},{"time":322000,"text":"Then this is a fairly talkative, verbose kind of chair."},{"time":330000,"text":"I also started meditating for the first time in my life in Bali."},{"time":334000,"text":"And at the same time, I'm extremely aware"},{"time":336000,"text":"how boring it is to hear about other people's happinesses."},{"time":340000,"text":"So I will not really go too far into it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345000,"text":"Many of you will know this TEDster,"},{"time":348000,"text":"Danny Gilbert, whose book, actually,"},{"time":350000,"text":"I got it through the TED book club."},{"time":352000,"text":"I think it took me four years"},{"time":354000,"text":"to finally read it, while on sabbatical."},{"time":358000,"text":"And I was pleased to see"},{"time":360000,"text":"that he actually wrote the book while he was on sabbatical."},{"time":364000,"text":"And I'll show you a couple of people"},{"time":366000,"text":"that did well by pursuing sabbaticals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"This is Ferran Adria. Many people think"},{"time":372000,"text":"he is right now the best chef in the world"},{"time":375000,"text":"with his restaurant north of Barcelona, El Bulli."},{"time":378000,"text":"His restaurant is open seven months every year."},{"time":380000,"text":"He closes it down for five months"},{"time":382000,"text":"to experiment with a full kitchen staff."},{"time":385000,"text":"His latest numbers are fairly impressive."},{"time":387000,"text":"He can seat, throughout the year,"},{"time":391000,"text":"he can seat 8,000 people."},{"time":394000,"text":"And he has 2.2 million requests for reservations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"If I look at my cycle, seven years, one year sabbatical,"},{"time":402000,"text":"it's 12.5 percent of my time."},{"time":405000,"text":"And if I look at companies that are actually more successful than mine,"},{"time":410000,"text":"3M since the 1930s"},{"time":413000,"text":"is giving all their engineers"},{"time":415000,"text":"15 percent to pursue whatever they want."},{"time":419000,"text":"There is some good successes."},{"time":421000,"text":"Scotch tape came out of this program,"},{"time":424000,"text":"as well as Art Fry developed"},{"time":428000,"text":"sticky notes from during his personal time for 3M."},{"time":432000,"text":"Google, of course, very famously"},{"time":434000,"text":"gives 20 percent for their software engineers"},{"time":436000,"text":"to pursue their own personal projects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"Anybody in here has actually ever conducted a sabbatical?"},{"time":446000,"text":"That's about five percent of everybody."},{"time":452000,"text":"So I'm not sure if you saw your neighbor putting their hand up."},{"time":456000,"text":"Talk to them about if it was successful or not."},{"time":460000,"text":"I've found that"},{"time":462000,"text":"finding out about what I'm going to like in the future,"},{"time":466000,"text":"my very best way is to talk to people"},{"time":468000,"text":"who have actually done it"},{"time":470000,"text":"much better than myself envisioning it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"When I had the idea of doing one,"},{"time":476000,"text":"the process was I made the decision and I put it into my daily planner book."},{"time":482000,"text":"And then I told as many, many people as I possibly could about it"},{"time":486000,"text":"so that there was no way that I could chicken out later on."},{"time":489000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"In the beginning, on the first sabbatical,"},{"time":494000,"text":"it was rather disastrous."},{"time":498000,"text":"I had thought that I should do this without any plan,"},{"time":502000,"text":"that this vacuum of time somehow would"},{"time":506000,"text":"be wonderful and enticing"},{"time":508000,"text":"for idea generation. It was not."},{"time":511000,"text":"I just, without a plan, I just reacted"},{"time":515000,"text":"to little requests, not work requests,"},{"time":518000,"text":"those I all said no to, but other little requests."},{"time":521000,"text":"Sending mail to Japanese design magazines and things like that."},{"time":524000,"text":"So I became my own intern."},{"time":526000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"And I very quickly"},{"time":531000,"text":"made a list of the things I was interested in,"},{"time":535000,"text":"put them in a hierarchy, divided them into chunks of time"},{"time":539000,"text":"and then made a plan, very much like in grade school."},{"time":543000,"text":"What does it say here? Monday, 8 to 9: story writing;"},{"time":547000,"text":"9 to 10: future thinking."},{"time":549000,"text":"Was not very successful. And so on and so forth."},{"time":552000,"text":"And that actually, specifically as a starting point"},{"time":554000,"text":"of the first sabbatical, worked really well for me."},{"time":557000,"text":"What came out of it?"},{"time":559000,"text":"I really got close to design again."},{"time":561000,"text":"I had fun."},{"time":563000,"text":"Financially, seen over the long term, it was actually successful."},{"time":566000,"text":"Because of the improved quality, we could ask for higher prices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571000,"text":"And probably most importantly,"},{"time":573000,"text":"basically everything we've done"},{"time":575000,"text":"in the seven years following the first sabbatical"},{"time":577000,"text":"came out of thinking of that one single year."},{"time":581000,"text":"And I'll show you a couple of projects"},{"time":584000,"text":"that came out of the seven years following that sabbatical."},{"time":589000,"text":"One of the strands of thinking I was involved in was"},{"time":593000,"text":"that sameness is so incredibly overrated."},{"time":595000,"text":"This whole idea that everything needs to be exactly the same"},{"time":599000,"text":"works for a very very few strand of companies,"},{"time":602000,"text":"and not for everybody else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604000,"text":"We were asked to design an identity for Casa da Musica,"},{"time":608000,"text":"the Rem Koolhaas-built music center"},{"time":611000,"text":"in Porto, in Portugal."},{"time":613000,"text":"And even though I desired to do an identity"},{"time":617000,"text":"that doesn't use the architecture,"},{"time":621000,"text":"I failed at that."},{"time":623000,"text":"And mostly also because I realized"},{"time":626000,"text":"out of a Rem Koolhaas presentation to the city of Porto, where"},{"time":629000,"text":"he talked about a conglomeration of various layers of meaning."},{"time":633000,"text":"Which I understood after I"},{"time":635000,"text":"translated it from architecture speech"},{"time":637000,"text":"in to regular English,"},{"time":639000,"text":"basically as logo making."},{"time":641000,"text":"And I understood that the building itself was a logo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644000,"text":"So then it became quite easy."},{"time":646000,"text":"We put a mask on it,"},{"time":648000,"text":"looked at it deep down in the ground,"},{"time":650000,"text":"checked it out from all sides,"},{"time":653000,"text":"west, north, south, east,"},{"time":656000,"text":"top and bottom."},{"time":658000,"text":"Colored them in a very particular way"},{"time":660000,"text":"by having a friend of mine write a piece of software,"},{"time":663000,"text":"the Casa da Musica Logo Generator."},{"time":665000,"text":"That's connected to a scanner."},{"time":668000,"text":"You put any image in there, like that Beethoven image."},{"time":671000,"text":"And the software, in a second,"},{"time":674000,"text":"will give you the Casa da Musica Beethoven logo."},{"time":677000,"text":"Which, when you actually have to design a Beethoven poster,"},{"time":680000,"text":"comes in handy, because the visual information of the logo"},{"time":685000,"text":"and the actual poster is exactly the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688000,"text":"So it will always fit together, conceptually, of course."},{"time":692000,"text":"If Zappa's music is performed, it gets its own logo."},{"time":696000,"text":"Or Philip Glass or Lou Reed or the Chemical Brothers,"},{"time":699000,"text":"who all performed there, get their own"},{"time":701000,"text":"Casa da Musica logo."},{"time":703000,"text":"It works the same internally with the president or the musical director,"},{"time":707000,"text":"whose Casa da Musica portraits wind up on their business cards."},{"time":711000,"text":"There is a full-blown orchestra"},{"time":713000,"text":"living inside the building."},{"time":716000,"text":"It has a more transparent identity."},{"time":720000,"text":"The truck they go on tour with."},{"time":723000,"text":"Or there's a smaller contemporary orchestra,"},{"time":726000,"text":"12 people that remixes its own title."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"And one of the handy things that came about"},{"time":734000,"text":"was that you could take the logo type"},{"time":737000,"text":"and create advertising out of it."},{"time":740000,"text":"Like this Donna Toney poster,"},{"time":742000,"text":"or Chopin, or Mozart,"},{"time":744000,"text":"or La Monte Young."},{"time":746000,"text":"You can take the shape and make typography out of it."},{"time":750000,"text":"You can grow it underneath the skin."},{"time":752000,"text":"You can have a poster for a family event in front of the house,"},{"time":756000,"text":"or a rave underneath the house"},{"time":759000,"text":"or a weekly program,"},{"time":761000,"text":"as well as educational services."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"Second insight. So far, until that point I had"},{"time":768000,"text":"been mostly involved"},{"time":771000,"text":"or used the language of design"},{"time":773000,"text":"for promotional purposes,"},{"time":775000,"text":"which was fine with me."},{"time":777000,"text":"On one hand I have nothing against selling."},{"time":779000,"text":"My parents are both salespeople."},{"time":782000,"text":"But I did feel that"},{"time":784000,"text":"I spent so much time learning this language,"},{"time":786000,"text":"why do I only promote with it?"},{"time":789000,"text":"There must be something else."},{"time":791000,"text":"And the whole series of work came out of it."},{"time":793000,"text":"Some of you might have seen it."},{"time":795000,"text":"I showed some of it"},{"time":797000,"text":"at earlier TEDs before,"},{"time":799000,"text":"under the title \"Things I've Learned in My Life So Far.\""},{"time":802000,"text":"I'll just show two now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804000,"text":"This is a whole wall of bananas"},{"time":807000,"text":"at different ripenesses"},{"time":809000,"text":"on the opening day in this gallery in New York."},{"time":812000,"text":"It says, \"Self-confidence produces fine results.\""},{"time":816000,"text":"This is after a week."},{"time":818000,"text":"After two weeks,"},{"time":820000,"text":"three weeks, four weeks, five weeks."},{"time":823000,"text":"And you see the self confidence almost comes back,"},{"time":825000,"text":"but not quite."},{"time":829000,"text":"These are some pictures visitors sent to me."},{"time":832000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":833000,"text":"And then the city of Amsterdam"},{"time":835000,"text":"gave us a plaza and asked us to do something."},{"time":838000,"text":"We used the stone plates as a grid"},{"time":842000,"text":"for our little piece."},{"time":845000,"text":"We got 250,000 coins from the central bank,"},{"time":849000,"text":"at different darknesses."},{"time":851000,"text":"So we got brand new ones, shiny ones,"},{"time":853000,"text":"medium ones, and very old, dark ones."},{"time":857000,"text":"And with the help of 100 volunteers, over a week,"},{"time":861000,"text":"created this fairly floral typography"},{"time":866000,"text":"that spelled, \"Obsessions make my life worse"},{"time":868000,"text":"and my work better.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":870000,"text":"And the idea of course was to"},{"time":872000,"text":"make the type so precious"},{"time":875000,"text":"that as an audience"},{"time":877000,"text":"you would be in between,"},{"time":879000,"text":"\"Should I really take as much money as I can?"},{"time":881000,"text":"Or should I leave the piece intact as it is right now?\""},{"time":886000,"text":"While we built all this up"},{"time":888000,"text":"during that week, with the 100 volunteers,"},{"time":890000,"text":"a good number of the neighbors surrounding the plaza"},{"time":894000,"text":"got very close to it and quite loved it."},{"time":896000,"text":"So when it was finally done,"},{"time":898000,"text":"and in the first night"},{"time":900000,"text":"a guy came with big plastic bags"},{"time":902000,"text":"and scooped up as many coins as he could possibly carry,"},{"time":907000,"text":"one of the neighbors called the police."}]},{"cues":[{"time":909000,"text":"And the Amsterdam police"},{"time":911000,"text":"in all their wisdom,"},{"time":914000,"text":"came, saw,"},{"time":916000,"text":"and they wanted to protect the artwork."},{"time":918000,"text":"And they swept it all up and put it into custody"},{"time":921000,"text":"at police headquarters."},{"time":923000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":925000,"text":"I think you see, you see them sweeping. You see them sweeping right here."},{"time":928000,"text":"That's the police, getting rid of it all."},{"time":932000,"text":"So after eight hours"},{"time":934000,"text":"that's pretty much all that was left"},{"time":936000,"text":"of the whole thing."},{"time":938000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":940000,"text":"We are also working on the start of a bigger project in Bali."},{"time":943000,"text":"It's a movie about happiness."},{"time":945000,"text":"And here we asked some nearby pigs"},{"time":948000,"text":"to do the titles for us."},{"time":950000,"text":"They weren't quite slick enough."},{"time":952000,"text":"So we asked the goose to do it again,"},{"time":954000,"text":"and hoped she would do somehow,"},{"time":956000,"text":"a more elegant or pretty job."},{"time":959000,"text":"And I think she overdid it."},{"time":961000,"text":"Just a bit too ornamental."},{"time":964000,"text":"And my studio is very close to the monkey forest."},{"time":968000,"text":"And the monkeys in that monkey forest"},{"time":970000,"text":"looked, actually, fairly happy."},{"time":972000,"text":"So we asked those guys to do it again."},{"time":977000,"text":"They did a fine job, but had"},{"time":979000,"text":"a couple of readability problems."},{"time":984000,"text":"So of course whatever you don't really do yourself"},{"time":987000,"text":"doesn't really get done properly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":991000,"text":"That film we'll be working on for the next two years."},{"time":995000,"text":"So it's going to be a while."},{"time":998000,"text":"And of course you might think that"},{"time":1000000,"text":"doing a film on happiness"},{"time":1003000,"text":"might not really be worthwhile."},{"time":1005000,"text":"Then you can of course always"},{"time":1007000,"text":"go and see this guy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1009000,"text":"Video: (Laughter)"},{"time":1024000,"text":"And I'm happy I'm alive."},{"time":1026000,"text":"I'm happy I'm alive. I'm happy I'm alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033000,"text":"Stefan Sagmeister: Thank you."},{"time":1035000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}